patthana15.65:4.1: Arūpāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naarūpāvacaro nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana15.65:4.2: Naarūpāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naarūpāvacaro nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana15.65:5.1: Naarūpāvacaraṃ akusalaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naarūpāvacaro naakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
